  "story": "A deeply personal devotional keerthanam declaring Jesus as the one true Saviour. Widely sung in Kerala's Marthoma and CSI congregations, this hymn expresses the intimate relationship between the believer and Christ. Its simple confession of faith has strengthened generations of Kerala Christians.",
